{
  "stem": "4187.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I found out, then, one day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I sure found out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Well, I mean-- I mean, about my-- about our background.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that was at school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I-- I had a pretty good school record.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I was captain of-- of the class.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Actually, all, sort of all-- when I say, always, I mean, from the time when we had captains.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then, and-- and there was a-- there was some sort of national day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I've reconstructed that in the last few days, actually.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There was a national day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I was given a rather prominent role to play in whatever was going on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And when all that was over, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my teacher, head teacher, said a few words to the class about me, which was awfully nice of her.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And next day, I was asked out from class and taken into a little room in the gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And there was the mother of one of my classmates, who was obviously beside herself, livid.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And she was screaming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And she was screaming at me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The moment I went in, she was screaming at me, 'dirty Jew.' How-- and she was saying to my teacher, 'how dare you put the--' not child of a dirty Jew.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just can't think of an-- a good equivalent word.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A brat, maybe, but even worse. 'The brat of a dirty Jew above my Aryan daughter?' 'How dare you keep her as exam--' oh, whatever it was, you know-- to-- to-- to hold her as an example or whatever?",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this went on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This went on for God knows how long.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I kept-- I-- I-- I wanted to interrupt and say, but, you know, you're wrong.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're wrong.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, of course, I didn't have a chance.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyhow, I started crying, naturally.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
